Sentencas: This study investigated the electrical conductivity and microstructure of samples with compositions Ce1-xGdxO2-delta (x = 0, 5, 10 and 15% in mol) prepared with CeO2 with 99.9% purity.
Titulo: Gd2O3 doped ceria electrolytes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The sintering of the samples obtained by isostatic pressing was performed in air at 1450 for 2 and 10 hours soaking time and 1500 degrees C for 8 hours of soaking time.
Titulo: Gd2O3 doped ceria electrolytes for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Sintered samples were characterized by scanning electron microscopy and impedance spectroscopy between 200-600 degrees C and the frequency range was 5Hz-13MHz.

Sentencas: The sintering occurred via liquid phase.

Sentencas: The 1450 degrees C with 10 h sintered samples showed more than 97% density.
